steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi003" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi003" display
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolstring" Type "string" for Table name "jitapi003" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicoltext" Type "text" for Table name "jitapi003" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolinteger" Type "integer" for Table name "jitapi003" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolfloat" Type "float" for Table name "jitapi003" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolenum" Type "enum_type" for Table name "jitapi003" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicoldate" Type "date" for Table name "jitapi003" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicoldatetime" Type "datetime" for Table name "jitapi003" and verify
When I navigate to menu "API endpoints" with submenu "API endpoints editor"
Then I should see API screen display
When I select api name "jitapi003s" from list
